them every couple of years.

00:23:30.380 --> 00:23:33.230
They're books by
Lloyd Alexander.

00:23:33.230 --> 00:23:38.107
And then after that it was
everything I could find.

00:23:38.107 --> 00:23:40.190
One sister got me "The
Lord of the Rings" one year

00:23:40.190 --> 00:23:42.260
when I was sick in
first grade, and I

00:23:42.260 --> 00:23:44.630
