year, we had to have

00:24:55.180 --> 00:24:56.884
a hand truck and
a bunch of crates

00:24:56.884 --> 00:24:58.550
to bring home all the
books that she had

00:24:58.550 --> 00:25:00.362
confiscated from me that year.

00:25:00.362 --> 00:25:02.820
