you know what-- he

00:25:05.890 --> 00:25:07.200
seems to be getting the lesson.

00:25:07.200 --> 00:25:10.250
Maybe we should
just let him read.

00:25:10.250 --> 00:25:12.960
They just sat me at the back
so I could read quietly and not

00:25:12.960 --> 00:25:15.304
